{"tid":2123231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逾29萬人過去數月入境香港後獲豁免強制檢疫14日","createTime":"2020-07-24T13:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T13:38:36.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9c55df5858d1e1941b714cdffb49183d9064ccc","tid":2123231,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:16:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539729-20200724.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539729-20200724.htm&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxRjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=a5cbd4cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539729-20200724.htm&h=f95390b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539729-20200724.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9dc3b2aa71857a9328773962e573d8b38825953c","tid":2123231,"uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"衞生署回本覆本台查詢時表示，當局6月於各出入境管制站，向45953名獲豁免檢疫的人士發出醫學監察通知書，較5月份多5733人，亦是自3月以來最多的月份。本月截至22日，則向39584人發出有關通知書。<br />\n<br />\n保安局本月8日書面回覆立法會議員提問時透露，政府由2月至5月一共向約20萬人發出通知書。換言之，由2月至前日，有29萬4千多人入境後毋須接受強制檢疫14日，但要接受14天醫學監察，期間須佩戴口罩和每天量度體溫兩次。"},{"pid":"3c6d790ec53b05f605dd1a68f3777bbe216c4e1d","tid":2123231,"uid":166445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"話撚左 跟本政府搞出離"},{"pid":"0d16a302edf59ce3e41ba91f7b4b1c50215436dd","tid":2123231,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"29萬人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face